snippet.title: Cube Escape: Birthday | Official trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to your 9th birthday, winter 1939. There is cake, music and a mysterious present. However, the mood changes quickly when an unexpected guest arrives at your party.

Download now for iOS (Iphone and Ipad):
https://itunes.apple.com/app/id1080643308
Download on Android:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=air.com.RustyLake.CubeEscapeBirthday
Or play on web:
http://www.rustylake.com/room-escape-games/cube-escape-birthday.html

Cube Escape: Birthday is the seventh episode of the Cube Escape series and is a continuation of the Rusty Lake story. We will unfold Rusty Lake mysteries one step at a time. So check RustyLake.com every day for new content.

Like and follow:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/rustylakecom
Twitter: https://twitter.com/rustylakecom
And subscribe to our mailing list: http://eepurl.com/bhphw1
